    </h2>
  
  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
          Submitted by Steven Devijver on Fri, 2006-05-19 15:40        </div>
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"> in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_6 first last active"><a href="/presentations" rel="tag" title="A link to a technical article about Spring" class="active">Technical Article</a></li>
</ul></div>
          </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    Dev2dev hosts an article on <a href="http://dev2dev.bea.com/pub/a/2006/05/declarative-caching.html" target="_self">Declarative Caching Services for Spring</a> written by <a href="http://www.jroller.com/page/alexRuiz" target="_self">Alex Ruiz</a>. This article discusses the Caching module in <a href="https://springmodules.dev.java.net/" target="_self">Spring Modules</a> which saw its <a href="https://springmodules.dev.java.net/servlets/ProjectDocumentList?folderID=5317&expandFolder=5317&folderID=0" target="_self">0.3 release</a> last week.<br /></i></strong></strong></i></b>  </div>

